{
  "stem": "21786.8",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was always-- I mean, it repeat itself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every second week, we got Romejko, Officer Romejko.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got the same story, and we got the same peace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then it was end of 1944 when there was-- came a new SS man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a youngish guy who had a little trace of French in his German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was one of the types like this SS man [INAUDIBLE] in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He would simply leave us-- lead us out without counting, without nothing, no signature, no nothing, no report.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He didn't want to have anything reported.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the first time we were on the way to the laundry, so he said to me, what is actually the best bartering commodity one can give you?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, Officer, why would you give us anything?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, oh, for I feel like it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not everyone has to be like the rest you are accustomed to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So just to test him I said, the best bartering commodities are cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We can buy anything for cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just to see what will happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The man disappeared, but came back to the laundry in about half an hour and gave me a box of 200 cigarettes. 200 cigarettes?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's like if you would get-- I don't know-- a car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was an unbelievable-- unbelievable fortune.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For three cigarettes, one could buy half a loaf of bread from the civilian prisoners.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said to him, Officer, first of all, I don't know how to thank you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have no means.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We have no means to repay anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And beside that, how do we get it into the camp?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, number one, you can hide it here and use it.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
